Remove items from a Fibery collection relation field.
Use this tool for explicit unlink/remove operations.

Safety requirement:
- `confirm_unlink` must be true.

Example:
{
    "database": "Kanban/Card",
    "entity_id": "ea5a9b77-d16b-4bdc-b4f2-5dad6764ad0f",
    "field": "assignments/assignees",
    "item_ids": [
        "f2a89e59-6a5a-439c-ab10-5e376548e8c9"
    ],
    "confirm_unlink": true
}
